snippet.title: DZMM TeleRadyo: Duterte accounts had P2.4-B in transactions: Trillanes

localized.description:
Presidential race frontrunner Rodrigo Duterte has bank transactions amounting to P2.407 billion, Sen. Antonio Trillanes IV claimed Friday.
